      <title>再生元制药遭遇法律挫折 遭遇两年来最糟糕一个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/regeneron-regn-set-for-big-monthly-drop-on-amgen-amgn-biosimilar-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[再生元制药公司 (Regeneron Pharmaceuticals Inc.) 股价有望创下 2019 年年中以来的最大月度跌幅，原因是该公司遭遇法律挫折，这为提前推出与其重磅眼科治疗药物 Eylea 竞争的疗法打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/regeneron-regn-set-for-big-monthly-drop-on-amgen-amgn-biosimilar-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:48:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
